        "subject": "LU-7659 mdc: add an ioctl call to the copytool char device",
        "message": "LU-7659 mdc: add an ioctl call to the copytool char device\n\nPrevisouly the offset of the read method was used to tell the copytool\nchar device what the archive_mask of the copytool char device was.\nNow we use an ioctl at register time to set that archive_mask.\n\nSigned-off-by: Quentin Bouget <quentin.bouget.ocre@cea.fr>\nChange-Id: I2eb551a096f188d1ed0363653cedc0d077132085\n"
      },
